children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {General Ledger,Annual Statistical Budget}

testSteps.description: Then the 'Statistical Entry - Annual Budget' should show up
When I set the Line Description to 'TEST1'
When I click on Continue button
Then the 'Statistical Entry Details - Anual Budget' should show up
When I set the Account Number to '01'
When I set the Units to '1000'
When I set the Cost Center to 'MAN5000'
When I set the Description to 'TEST1'
When I click on Save button
Then the 'Statistical Budget Entry successfully created' modal should show up
